This kinda works ```&lt;nav class="solutions-hero__nav"&gt;
	{% set totalNum = solutions|length %}
	{% set navPos = 0 %}
	{% for nav in solutions %}
		{% if request.path == nav.url %}
			{% set navPos = navPos|add(loop.index) %}
		{% endif %}
	{% endfor %}
	{{ totalNum }} - 
		{{ navPos }}
	{% if navPos &gt; 1 %}
		&lt;a href=""&gt;{{ solutions[navPos|add(-1)].title }}&lt;/a&gt;
	{% endif %}
	{% if navPos &lt; totalNum %}
		&lt;a href=""&gt;{{ solutions[navPos|add(1)].title }}&lt;/a&gt;
	{% endif %}
&lt;/nav&gt;```

